  "title": "Purchasing Admin (Labrador Park) - 1 year contract renewable",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Issue invoices and update the receivables list accurately.</li><li>Prepare purchase orders and requisitions using software.</li><li>Obtain business profiles and financial information from BizFile.</li><li>Verify and process monthly staff claims.</li><li>Manage office supplies, including stationery and pantry stock.</li><li>Answer phone calls and attend to visitors professionally.</li><li>Handle filing, scanning, and other administrative documentation.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.                                                      </li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel, PowerPoint).</li><li>Familiarity with Workbench software is an advantage.</li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.\nAbility to work independently and as part of a team.\nDetail-oriented with good organizational skills.                                                            </li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the above positions, please click \"Apply now\" <br /><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. </p><p>JAC Recruitment Pte. Ltd. </p><p>EA License No: 90C3026<br />EA Personnel No: R23113652<br />EA Personnel Name: Wong Yi Lei</p>",
